{"tid":521662,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後自稱「旅遊達人」但連喜茶都未飲過！真係羞家！","createTime":"2018-01-06T18:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T13:56:42.000Z","uid":19334,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00fcb6bdd7fd029cffcb9b8853ac5507e305c7c9","tid":521662,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"話說黎緊下個禮拜難得請左一日AL，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就問下同事去邊玩邊到飲飲食食好(唔夠時間去日本)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁傾傾下好多人都Suggest我番大陸玩既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁平時我番大陸工幹都會去買番杯HEYTEA，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為暫時都搵唔到有芝士奶蓋好飲得過佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁討論期間見到隻90後無出過聲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我又留意到佢成日四圍玩(好似上個月去左歐遊，又自稱旅遊達人)！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪問下佢有咩好推介，有無好飲過喜茶既芝士奶蓋/水果茶，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢竟然話自己未飲過喜茶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地全場靜哂，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到自命識飲識食周圍去玩既旅遊達人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連「喜茶」都未飲過，真係羞家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2cfb1d62ebe2cc21f3bb3b3d8cdcaff53adaf7","tid":521662,"uid":96245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾 有工唔返走去請AL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915bfbf80ed98b936f296c4a01a7f498a5f93c4b","tid":521662,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1f2cfb1d62ebe2cc21f3bb3b3d8cdcaff53adaf7","tid":521662,"uid"